5. DISCUSSION AND INTERPRETATION OF RESULTS 
The introduction of  three additional dimensions Ñ chance, zero, and inf inityÑinto our understanding of  the universe offers a new 
perspective with wide -ranging implications.This section delves into the potential consequences of  the 
 
