2.
 
Riemann curvature tensor: 
R^{\mu}{\nu\sigma\rho} = \partial{\sigma} \Gamma^{\mu}{\nu\rho} - \partial{\rho} 
\Gamma^{\mu}{\nu\sigma} + \Gamma^{\mu}{\alpha\sigma} \Gamma^{\alpha}{\nu\rho} - 
\Gamma^{\mu}{\alpha\rho} \Gamma^{\alpha}_{\nu\sigma}. 
 
